('tld017','shop',
'<p>The <strong>.shop</strong> domain is tailored for <strong>retail and e-commerce</strong>. Operated by GMO Registry, it is especially popular in Asia and with international e-commerce brands.</p>',
'<p>Launched in 2016 by <strong>GMO Registry</strong>, .shop saw rapid adoption in Japan and internationally. It competes directly with .store for e-commerce brands.</p>',
