('tld023','tv',
'<p>The <strong>.tv</strong> domain is the ccTLD for <strong>Tuvalu</strong>, but has been globally adopted for <strong>television networks, streaming services, video content, and broadcasters</strong>.</p>',
'<p>Tuvalu''s .tv was delegated in 1996. In 2000, Tuvalu licensed .tv exclusively to <strong>dotTV (now VeriSign)</strong> for $50 million, transforming it into a globally marketed media domain.</p>',
'<p>Popular with:</p><ul><li><strong>TV networks and channels</strong></li><li><strong>Video streaming platforms</strong></li><li><strong>YouTube channels and video creators</strong></li><li><strong>Live streaming services</strong></li></ul>',
