'<p>Popular for:</p><ul><li><strong>Short brand URLs</strong></li><li><strong>Alternative to .com</strong></li><li><strong>Creative industry professionals</strong></li></ul>',
'[]',
'<p>Open to all worldwide. Cost: approximately <strong>$20–$30/year</strong>.</p>',
1,0,'system',NOW()),

('tld027','in',
'<p>The <strong>.in</strong> domain is the official ccTLD for <strong>India</strong>, the world''s most populous country and a rapidly growing digital economy. With over 2 million registrations, .in is one of Asia''s most active ccTLDs.</p>',
'<p>Delegated in 1989, .in is managed by <strong>INRegistry</strong> (operated by NIXI). India''s tech boom and digital growth have made .in increasingly relevant globally.</p>',
'<p>Used by:</p><ul><li><strong>Indian businesses and startups</strong></li><li><strong>Indian government portals</strong></li><li><strong>Global companies targeting the Indian market</strong></li></ul>',
'[{"name":"IRCTC","url":"irctc.co.in"},{"name":"Flipkart","url":"flipkart.com"}]',
'<p>Open to Indian residents and entities. Cost: approximately <strong>$5–$10/year</strong>.</p>',
1,0,'system',NOW()),

('tld028','de',
'<p>The <strong>.de</strong> domain is the official ccTLD for <strong>Germany</strong>. With over <strong>17 million registrations</strong>, it is the largest national ccTLD in the world, surpassing even many generic TLDs.</p>',
'<p>Delegated in 1986, .de is managed by <strong>DENIC eG</strong>, a cooperative of internet service providers. Germany''s strong economy and internet infrastructure have made .de one of the world''s most trusted country domains.</p>',
'<p>Used by:</p><ul><li><strong>German businesses of all sizes</strong></li><li><strong>Government and educational institutions</strong></li><li><strong>International companies targeting German customers</strong></li></ul>',
'[{"name":"SPIEGEL","url":"spiegel.de"},{"name":"BILD","url":"bild.de"},{"name":"Deutsche Bahn","url":"bahn.de"}]',
'<p>No geographic restriction — anyone can register .de. However, a <strong>local administrative contact in Germany</strong> may be required by some registrars. Cost: approximately <strong>$5–$10/year</strong>.</p>',
1,0,'system',NOW()),

('tld029','uk',
'<p>The <strong>.uk</strong> domain (and its subdomain <strong>.co.uk</strong>) is the official ccTLD for the <strong>United Kingdom</strong>. .co.uk is the traditional commercial domain used by UK businesses.</p>',
